with DDO_ISP_FACT_PROV_PGM_MIDDLE_T as ( SELECT PROV_ID,PGM_ID,OUTCOME_MEASURE_ID,OM_LABEL_ID,max(TIME_ID_WITHOUT_QUARTER) max_time_id FROM DDO_ISP_FACT_PROV_PGM_MIDDLE GROUP BY PROV_ID,PGM_ID, OUTCOME_MEASURE_ID,OM_LABEL_ID)
SELECT dt.PROV_ID, dt.PGM_ID, dit.id,dt.OUTCOME_MEASURE_ID,dt.om_LABEL_ID,0,max(dit.ID_WITHOUT_QUARTER) FROM DIM_ISP_TIME dit join DDO_ISP_FACT_PROV_PGM_MIDDLE_T dt on (dit.DAY_KEY > to_date(dt.max_time_id,'YYYYMM' ) and dit.DAY_KEY < (add_months(to_date(dt.max_time_id,'YYYYMM' ) , 12))) group by dt.PGM_ID,dt.PROV_ID,dit.ID,dt.OUTCOME_MEASURE_ID,dt.om_LABEL_ID,dit.ID_WITHOUT_QUARTER
